  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the raclette grill to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Spread a thin layer of coconut oil on the grill surface.",
    "Mix the yuzu juice and Greek yogurt in a small bowl.",
    "Pour the yuzu-yogurt mixture over 4-6 raclette cheese portions and top with crushed pistachios.",
    "Drizzle honey over the pistachios for the glaze.",
    "Place the cheese portions on the grill and cook for 3-4 minutes or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with additional pistachios and a drizzle of honey, if desired."
